Sentencas: To improve the performance of solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) interconnects, coatings on Crofer 22APU alloy were obtained by the combination of Fe-Ni-Co spinel oxides/Y2O3 and sol-gel method.
Titulo: Effect of nanostructure Fe-Ni-Co spinel oxides/Y2O3 coatings on the high-temperature oxidation behavior of Crofer 22 APU stainless steel interconnect

Sentencas: The cyclic oxidation of steels was carried out at 800 degrees C for 500 h, evaluating the samples' electrical conductivity in the air at 800 degrees C after 500 h of oxidation.
Titulo: Effect of nanostructure Fe-Ni-Co spinel oxides/Y2O3 coatings on the high-temperature oxidation behavior of Crofer 22 APU stainless steel interconnect

Sentencas: Findings indicated that the Fe-Ni-Co spinel oxides/Y2O3 coating could be a barrier to improving the steel oxidation resistance.
Titulo: Effect of nanostructure Fe-Ni-Co spinel oxides/Y2O3 coatings on the high-temperature oxidation behavior of Crofer 22 APU stainless steel interconnect

Sentencas: The surface scale's electrical conductivity on the coated steel was much higher than that on the bare steel.
Titulo: Effect of nanostructure Fe-Ni-Co spinel oxides/Y2O3 coatings on the high-temperature oxidation behavior of Crofer 22 APU stainless steel interconnect
